title: Parfum Culture
typeOfFood: Japanese, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Taiwanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Sushi, Japanese, and Asian food restaurant. Menu includes marked veg choices like tofu, vegetable gyoza, and vegetable stir fry. Staff will assist explain which items are veg suitable. Comfortable place. Menu from 10-40 euros with options for "sake lovers." Closed August month.
